Minesweeper clone for the Meggy Jr RGB.

Changelog:
 
  Version 1.1, 31-May-2009
  - Added button repeat (can hold down d-buttons).
  - Added first-click immunity.
  - Now smaller and with less repeated code.

  Version 1.0, 31-May-2009
  - Initial version.
   
